cinnamon.engine.utils

Class Assets

  • java.lang.Object
    • cinnamon.engine.utils.Assets

  • public final class Assets
extends Object

    File and resource loading utility class. Load methods come in both synchronous and asynchronous flavors with the latter versions denoted by the suffix 'Async'. Currently, only String and byte[] loading outputs are provided.
